ke":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T09:47:55.000Z","msg":"日本發佈戰略目標：2025年確立6G技術<br />\n<br />\n　　日本總務省4月8日發佈了2025年在日本國內確立「6G」主要技術的戰略目標。6G高速通信標準是「5G」的下一代。著眼於2030年代的6G實用化，日本將通過稅收優惠等構建走在世界前列的開發環境。計劃以國立研究開發法人「信息通信研究機構」為中心，成立産官學（即企業、政府和高校）展開合作的新組織，主導6G國際標準制定的相關討論。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.cn.nikkei.com/industry/scienceatechnology/40128-2020-04-09-11-29-05.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.cn.nikkei.com%2Findustry%2Fscienceatechnology%2F40128-2020-04-09-11-29-05.html&d=eQX%2BqlmYp67lP1AM6ayufQmnwACYIcySctyK7icvN2A%3D&h=6df6e4e4\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.cn.nikkei.com/industry/scienceatechnology/40128-2020-04-09-11-29-05.html</a>"},{"pid":"10fc321b1129e94087d1bc3b539510028718f99a","tid":1998050,"uid":46493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4bf1cfbdd6dee97d1d407c20340fed58b4456009","tid":1998050,"uid":187112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T06:20:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://technews.tw/2020/04/27/spacex-to-offer-starlink-public-beta-in-six-months-musk-says/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftechnews.tw%2F2020%2F04%2F27%2Fspacex-to-offer-starlink-public-beta-in-six-months-musk-says%2F&d=eQX%2BqlmYp67lP1AM6ayufQmnwACYIcySctyK7icvN2A%3D&h=37051392\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://technews.tw/2020/04/27/spacex-to-offer-starlink-public-beta-in-six-months-musk-says/</a><br />\n<br />\n如題。"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T10:12:47.000Z","msg":"慢同delay先係最大問題"},{"pid":"110ba3699ff8b77b7fd332cb0707ba330add3354","tid":1998050,"uid":31237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"732a9eab44aebbb24cd3a416dfd3680ced8d7fde","tid":1998050,"uid":295224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T08:57:21.000Z","msg":"唔知中國可唔可以用 如果可以咁樣佢地咪可以唔洗理幅西牆 同埋同文明世界流通囉"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T10:17:48.000Z","msg":"好似美國之音經衛星播fm咁"},{"pid":"4e7bcf3a6a0ca1c1e48d4e2758d6fe133f427779","tid":1998050,"uid":157987,"like":0,"