span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nSpaceX的「星鏈衛星網路計劃」是藉由在靠近地球的軌道，建立大量用於通訊的衛星網路來提升地球網路速度。首次針對該計畫發射是在2018年2月22日，至今已是SpaceX第七次成功針對此計畫，完成太空網路衛星的發射。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">該計畫共有約12000顆衛星需送入軌道，而目前SpaceX已將計劃中的420顆送入軌道。</span></strong></strong><br />\n<br />\nSpaceX執行長伊隆&middot;馬斯克（Elon Musk）表示只要約400顆衛星，其實就能提供初步網路。因此，這次的發射也代表著SpaceX現在擁有啟動計畫所需的最低衛星數"},{"pid":"7d3accd92aabb9cf24615850bf91a1660b6e9dfe","tid":1998050,"uid":35347,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"732a9eab44aebbb24cd3a416dfd3680ced8d7fde","tid":1998050,"uid":295224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T08:57:21.000Z","msg":"唔知中國可唔可以用 如果可以咁樣佢地咪可以唔洗理幅西牆 同埋同文明世界流通囉"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T10:43:17.000Z","msg":"Starlink要裝地面基站<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"770e68f062e1246e4e29d23fa59378b1a49f880e","tid":1998050,"uid":30104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"10fc321b1129e94087d1bc3b539510028718f99a","tid":1998050,"uid":46493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4bf1cfbdd6dee97d1d407c20340fed58b4456009","tid":1998050,"uid":187112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T06:20:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://technews.tw/2020/04/27/spacex-to-offer-starlink-public-beta-in-six-months-musk-says/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftechnews.tw%2F2020%2F04%2F27%2Fspacex-to-offer-starlink-public-beta-in-six-months-musk-says%2F&d=eQX%2BqlmYp67lP1AM6ayufQmnwACYIcySctyK7icvN2A%3D&h=37051392\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://technews.tw/2020/04/27/spacex-to-offer-starlink-public-beta-in-six-months-musk-says/</a><br />\n<br />\n如題。"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T10:12:47.000Z","msg":"慢同delay先係最大問題"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T10:45:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 太空傳送data 比光纖更低delay"},{"pid":"3b7176d3d11b5febf372a4e100c0c24845b9ef7b","tid":1998050,"uid":187112,